        </div>
        <div class="sdbp-concept">
          <span class="sdbp-concept-icon">🧠</span>
          <p class="sdbp-concept-title">DBT Skills</p>
          <p class="sdbp-concept-text">Equips you with practical mindfulness, distress tolerance, and emotional regulation strategies for daily life.</p>
        </div>
